item.title: When Your Network is Down
item.itunes:author: Pastor Mike Gonzalez
item.itunes:summary: Marriages and other relationships cant survive without effective communication. Effective communication cant survivemuch less deepenunless we give each other a safe place to share feelings as well as facts.

item.title: Fit to be Tied
item.itunes:author: Pastor Mike Gonzalez
item.itunes:summary: Anger isnt wrong in itself, but expressing it in the wrong way can destroy relationships. Taking the Bibles advice on anger can preserve marriages, friendships, and family bonds.
